components.templateData:
<container
  type="QuartzCron"
  value="0,1,2 2/4 6/2 ? 2-7 SUN,MON 2019/1"
  #quartzContainer>

  <ng-template
    #content
    let-value="value"
    let-cssClassPrefix="cssClassPrefix"
    let-localization="localization"
    let-activeTab="activeTab"
    let-tabs="tabs"
    let-hideTabs="hideTabs"
    let-disabled="disabled">

    <quartz-cron
      [cssClassPrefix]="cssClassPrefix"
      [localization]="localization"
      [activeTab]="activeTab"
      [tabs]="tabs"
      [hideTabs]="hideTabs"
      [disabled]="disabled"
      [ngModel]="value"
      (changed)="quartzContainer.updateValue($event)"
      (tabChanged)="quartzContainer.updateActiveTab($event)">
    </quartz-cron>
  </ng-template>
</container>

<container
  type="UnixCron"
  value="0 4 8-14 * *"
  [initialTabs]="[tab.MINUTES, tab.HOURS, tab.DAY, tab.MONTH]"
  #unixContainer>

  <ng-template
    #content
    let-value="value"
    let-cssClassPrefix="cssClassPrefix"
    let-localization="localization"
    let-activeTab="activeTab"
    let-tabs="tabs"
    let-hideTabs="hideTabs"
    let-disabled="disabled">

    <unix-cron
      [cssClassPrefix]="cssClassPrefix"
      [localization]="localization"
      [activeTab]="activeTab"
      [tabs]="tabs"
      [hideTabs]="hideTabs"
      [disabled]="disabled"
      [ngModel]="value"
      (changed)="unixContainer.updateValue($event)"
      (tabChanged)="unixContainer.updateActiveTab($event)">
    </unix-cron>
  </ng-template>
</container>

<container
  type="Bs5QuartzCron"
  value="0,1,2 2/4 6/2 ? 2-7 SUN,MON 2019/1"
  #bs5QuartzContainer>

  <ng-template
    #content
    let-value="value"
    let-cssClassPrefix="cssClassPrefix"
    let-localization="localization"
    let-activeTab="activeTab"
    let-tabs="tabs"
    let-hideTabs="hideTabs"
    let-disabled="disabled">

    <quartz-cron
      [styles]="cronBootstrap5"
      [cssClassPrefix]="cssClassPrefix"
      [localization]="localization"
      [activeTab]="activeTab"
      [tabs]="tabs"
      [hideTabs]="hideTabs"
      [disabled]="disabled"
      [ngModel]="value"
      (changed)="bs5QuartzContainer.updateValue($event)"
      (tabChanged)="bs5QuartzContainer.updateActiveTab($event)">
    </quartz-cron>
  </ng-template>
</container>

<container
  type="Bs5UnixCron"
  value="0 4 8-14 * *"
  [initialTabs]="[tab.MINUTES, tab.HOURS, tab.DAY, tab.MONTH]"
  #bs5UnixContainer>

  <ng-template
    #content
    let-value="value"
    let-cssClassPrefix="cssClassPrefix"
    let-localization="localization"
    let-activeTab="activeTab"
    let-tabs="tabs"
    let-hideTabs="hideTabs"
    let-disabled="disabled">

    <unix-cron
      [styles]="cronBootstrap5"
      [cssClassPrefix]="cssClassPrefix"
      [localization]="localization"
      [activeTab]="activeTab"
      [tabs]="tabs"
      [hideTabs]="hideTabs"
      [disabled]="disabled"
      [ngModel]="value"
      (changed)="bs5UnixContainer.updateValue($event)"
      (tabChanged)="bs5UnixContainer.updateActiveTab($event)">
    </unix-cron>
  </ng-template>
</container>
